FBIS3-14756 "drsov039_f_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 National Affairs Diplomat Denies Kravchuk Refusal to Run LD2702152694 Moscow Radio Moscow World Service in English 1200 GMT 27 Feb 94 LD2702152694 Moscow Radio Moscow World Service Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Ukrainian ambassador to Russia, Volodymyr Kryzhanovshyy, refuted a report that Leonid Kravchuk has refused to take part in the upcoming presidential elections of the republic. In his words, Ukrainian president came out in favor of postponing the election of the head of state. If his opinion is disregarded, he may refuse to run for presidency, said Kryzhanovshyy.
